_header: God that all thing first began
_description: ‘Templum Domini’: An Englishing of Grosseteste’s treatise — 784 lines in 8-line stanzas

BLAdd32578.First Lines:
Gode þat all thynge first beganHas giffen his grace in diuerse
                    gyse…
BLAdd32578.Last Lines:
…Als he of noȝt all thynges be ganGif vs ȝe blisse
                    þat lastes ay
